citation: Retirement Benefits (State Fire Commission Superannuation Scheme) Act 2005 (Repealed) (Tas)
text:
Retirement Benefits (State Fire Commission Superannuation Scheme) Act 2005 (Repealed)

1. (Repealed)
    The Retirement Benefits (State Fire Commission Superannuation Scheme) Act 2005 has been repealed by Schedule 4 to the Public Sector Superannuation Reform Act 2016
